---
title: One-Pot Kidney Bean & Pepper Soup with Blue Corn Tortilla Chips, Monterey Jack & Sour Cream
description: Soup-er supper alert! Just one spoonful of this hearty, richly spiced soup will warm you from the inside out. Kidney beans simmer with Southwest spices, sautéed onion, and green pepper until thickened. The soup’s then served loaded up with all the fixin’s: sour cream, Monterey Jack cheese, and cilantro, plus blue corn tortilla chips on the side for dipping. Oh, happy belly!
